{"title_page": "S\u00e9rgio Santos (footballer, born 1998)", "text_new": "{{short description|Portuguese professional footballer}}\n\n{{distinguish|Sergio Santos (footballer, born 1994)}}\n\n{{similar names|Sergio Santos (disambiguation)}}\n\n{{refimprove|date=December 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = S\u00e9rgio Santos\n| image          =\n| fullname       = S\u00e9rgio Assis Capitango Fernando Santos\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1998|10|2}}\n| birth_place    = [[Lisbon]], Portugal\n| height         = 1.80\n| position       = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub    = [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]]\n| clubnumber     = 79\n| years1         = 2017\u20132019 | clubs1 = [[S.C. Pinheiro de Loures|Loures]] | caps1 = 1 | goals1 = 0\n| years2         = 2019\u2013     | clubs2 = [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] | caps2 = 0  | goals2 = 0\n| totalcaps      = \n| totalgoals     = \n| medaltemplates = \n| pcupdate       = 15 December 2019\n}}\n\n'''S\u00e9rgio Assis Capitango Fernando Santos''' (born 2 October 1998) is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]].\n\n==Professional career==\nSantos made his professional debut with [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] in a 2-1 [[Ta\u00e7a da Liga]] win over [[Gil Vicente F.C.]] on 25 September 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2019/09/25/portugal/league-cup/gil-vicente-fc/portimonense-sc/3162528/|title=Gil Vicente vs. Portimonense - 25 September 2019 - Soccerway|website=ca.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.zerozero.pt/player.php?id=277161 S\u00e9rgio Santos] at ZeroZero.pt\n\n{{Portimonense S.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Santos, S\u00e9rgio}}\n[[Category:1998 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Lisbon]]\n[[Category:Portuguese footballers]]\n[[Category:Portuguese people of Cape Verdean descent]]\n[[Category:Portimonense S.C. players]]\n[[Category:Primeira Liga players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Portuguese professional footballer}}\n\n{{distinguish|Sergio Santos (footballer, born 1994)}}{{similar names|Sergio Santos (disambiguation)}}\n\n{{refimprove|date=December 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = S\u00e9rgio Santos\n| image          =\n| fullname       = S\u00e9rgio Assis Capitango Fernando Santos\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1998|10|2}}\n| birth_place    = [[Lisbon]], Portugal\n| height         = 1.80\n| position       = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub    = [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]]\n| clubnumber     = 79\n| years1         = 2017\u20132019 | clubs1 = [[S.C. Pinheiro de Loures|Loures]] | caps1 = 1 | goals1 = 0\n| years2         = 2019\u2013     | clubs2 = [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] | caps2 = 0  | goals2 = 0\n| totalcaps      = \n| totalgoals     = \n| medaltemplates = \n| pcupdate       = 15 December 2019\n}}\n\n'''S\u00e9rgio Assis Capitango Fernando Santos''' (born 2 October 1998) is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]].\n\n==Professional career==\nSantos made his professional debut with [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] in a 2-1 [[Ta\u00e7a da Liga]] win over [[Gil Vicente F.C.]] on 25 September 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2019/09/25/portugal/league-cup/gil-vicente-fc/portimonense-sc/3162528/|title=Gil Vicente vs. Portimonense - 25 September 2019 - Soccerway|website=ca.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.zerozero.pt/player.php?id=277161 S\u00e9rgio Santos] at ZeroZero.pt\n\n{{Portimonense S.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Santos, S\u00e9rgio}}\n[[Cate